meta {
  name: List price-list
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

get {
  url: {{host}}/api/{{bu_code}}/price-list
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

headers {
  x-app-id: {{x_app_id}}
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{access_token}}
}

query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## Get All Price Lists
  แสดงรายการราคาทั้งหมดของหน่วยธุรกิจ พร้อมการแบ่งหน้าและค้นหา

  Lists all active vendor price lists for the business unit, allowing procurement staff to browse current pricing agreements and compare vendor offerings.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `page` | number | No | 1 | Page number |
  | `perpage` | number | No | 10 | Items per page |
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `vendor_management.price_list:view`
  - **Roles**: Requestor, HOD, Purchase, Approval

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
