  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Bearer token missing or invalid |
  | 403 | User lacks `vendor_management.price_list:view` permission |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}
